title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Feb 18 2022

description:
BLM bails out assassin who shot at Jewish Louisville mayoral candidate: No outrage after BLM crowdfunds $100,000 bail to free former MSNBC guest Quintez Brown, while Canada shuts down crowdfunding donations to the trucker convoy and non-violent January 6th protesters still sit in jail. NYC crime wave and The Squad. Fauci continues to spread mask misinformation. Buck, a known "mask prophet," gives a vivid "from afar psychology diagnosis" of who Clay calls "the evil dictator of medicine." Will Biden be the Democrat nominee in 2024? Who's more likable, Hillary or Kamala? Clay asks how it's possible Harris' polls are so low even in "Cali-freakin-fornia!"
